<plot>Two are together, yet they do not talk, they do not play like they used to, they are completely silent. For one is lost in his thoughts, his memories, the cloud of sadness that is wrapped in the memory of the other. As the loss begins to settle upon the broken heart of one sibling, the deceased begins his own journey to be remembered. A touching story about one day when a spirit can return and haunt.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?510599</url></doc>
